node.text: looking beautiful Maya, made my day💜

many of my favorite restaurants are on DELIVERY! 🥰 circuit breaker might be ending, but we are encouraged to stay home often. order from the restaurants directly to save!
________
1️⃣ throwback to #BunCha at hanoi airport (need recommendations for viet food delivery!)
_
2️⃣ @brotherbird_bakehouse highly sought after artisanal croissants! crispy, huge & buttery. addictive with trending flavors eg: boba milktea, dalgona coffee & more. box of 6 ($28) @ 1 box per person. get via google form on their FB. slots got snatched in less than a min. islandwide delivery at $10.
_
3️⃣ @gonoodlehousesg - heavenly bursting pork meatballs in signature broth made with more than 40 types of fish bones! whatsapp +65 9733 7323 or https://gonoodle.oddle.me/en_SG to order. min order @ $35, $5 islandwide delivery.
_
4️⃣ @weenamkee_sg - hainanese chicken rice with tasty tze cha dishes at affordable prices. whatsapp +65 9833 2019 or @grabfoodsg to order. min order @ $30, free islandwide delivery.
_
5️⃣ @papparichsg - familiar asian dishes eg: nasi lemak, curry laksa, KL hokkien mee & more! https://papparich.oddle.me/en_SG or whatsapp at 65 9732 7323 to order. minimum order @ $35, $5 islandwide delivery.
_
6️⃣ @kopifellas - traditional coffees, teas, toasts, & hot mains for lunch & tea break. min order @ $12, $5 next day delivery.
_
7️⃣ @mongasingapore - 2cm thick fried chicken with sides, rice boxes & bubble teas. whatsapp +65 8896 5136 to order. min order @ $30, free islandwide delivery. 
_
8️⃣ @blackandink - café offering creative dishes, lattes & cakes. signature Char Bowl garners cha siew from famous @roastparadise. http://blackandink.sg or whatsapp +65 8749 9929 to order. min order @ $30. free delivery for $50 & more.
_
9️⃣ @whitebeehoonrestaurant - homely dishes with seafood broth white bee hoon as signature. add sambal chill for extra oomph! https://order.whiterestaurant.com.sg or @grabfoodsg to order. min order @ $50. $4.90 islandwide delivery.
_
🔟 @breadtalksg - always in sync with baking trends. cute ROFL honey marble sponge alongside breads & cakes at https://www.breadtalk.com.sg/shop. no min purchase, $5 next day delivery, free with $30 & more.
—————
#savefnbSG
#SGunited
